originalText.text: Very satisfied with the professional work done by Fast Chimney Sweep & Repair And Fireplace Cleaning Services LLC. They are very honest, professional, and courteous. Jake were very thorough in explaining what needed to be done and kept me abreast while the work was being completed. I was not disappointed and recommend Fast Chimney Sweep & Repair And Fireplace Cleaning Serices LLC for their great service.

originalText.text: Very professional team. They did an excellent job, covered everything including their shoes, were very polite and thorough. Showed me pictures they took of inside of fireplace and outside on the roof and answered all questions I had. Would highly recommend Fast Chimney Sweep & Repair And Fireplace Cleaning Services LLC.

originalText.text:
Fast Rite came by and did a "house call" to get the info about an icemaker repair. I paid $90+ for the technician to locate an ID number on the appliance-no actual repair work took place on this call.

After nearly 3 months, Fast Rite still does not have the part to repair the ice maker.  After numerous phone attempts to get an update on the situation I was hung up on by the main contact at the company.  Now the phone is out of service.

As far as I am concerned Fast Rite STOLE $90+ from me.   I would NEVER EVER call this company again...did I mention NEVER!!!!
